reviewText: It says this was released in 2010 but the video looks like it is from 1980. The video quality is very low. The information I guess is good if you can ignore the cheesy music and bad video. This was definitely not made in 2010. I'm sure that there is something much better out there.
This DVD is a piece of junk. The quality is very, very low. I threw it to the garbage. I do not recommend it.
